      • update

        void update(RequestEvent message,
          RequestNotifier notifier)
        This method handles the updates received from the RequestNotifier. It gets the RequestEvent that specifies the current state of the RequestNotifier and a link to the notifier itself.
        Parameters:
        message - The state of the RequestNotifier, a RequestEvent
        notifier - The notifier itself
